                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "One Action"
                    },
                    "effect": "You call on the power of the warshard to load the  *screaming pinion* with a bullet made of divine fury. The next attack from the gun deals spirit damage, rather than its typical type, and on a critical hit, the target is subject to the weapon\u2019s critical specialization effect. If the gun isn\u2019t fired before the end of your next turn, the bullet disappears, and the gun becomes unloaded.",
                    "links": [
                        {
                            "type": "link",
                            "name": "spirit",
                            "alt": "spirit",
                            "game-obj": "Traits",
                            "aonid": 737
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "link",
                            "name": "critical specialization",
                            "alt": "critical specialization",
                            "game-obj": "Rules",
                            "aonid": 2203
                        }
                    ],
                    "requirement": "The  *screaming pinion* is unloaded",
